      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wisch arri man buhs\nar Pestischann/ jo weens Wilt-\nceks winna Preekfchâ ne nahks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Klaufajt tifkutchi mannu\nWallofu/ un mannu Jfstahsti-\nchanu ar jubfahm Ausjum.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rangi jelle/ es taifohs us\nTeesu/ es finnu/ ka es taifus\nuhfschu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas tas tahds irr/ kas ar\nnan grib teefatees? jo nu es kluſ-\nu zeetischu un nomirſchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Diwejas Leetas tikfai man\nne padarri/ tad es tawâ Preek-\nchâ ne apſlebpschohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Lai tawa Rohka tahtu\nno mannim paleek/ un tawa\nBreetmiba lai manni ne tsbeede.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fanz/ un es atbilde-\nchu/ jeb es runnaschu/ un tu at-\nbldi man.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zik man irr to Noseegu-\nnu un Grehku? darri man man-\nnas Pahrkahpschanas un man-\nnus Grehkus finnamus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kapehz apflep tu tawu\nWaigu/ un turri mann par ta-\nwu Eenaſdnceku?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Grib tu prett wennu\nfchaubigu Lappu tik bahrgi tur-\nretees/ un iſkaltuschus Rugga\njus wajaht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tu rakſti pahr manni\nRuhktumnus/ un leez man man-\nnas Jaunibas Noseegumus mat-\ntiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un leez mannas Kahjas\nSeckſa/ un nemm wiﬀus\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kur tomehr fchi (Meefa)\nka japuufi Maita isnihkt/ itt ka\nweena Drehbe/ fo Kohdas ehd.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XIV. Nodalla.\nFiabs apraksta itt krahschni/ ka ihja un nos-\nscheblojama to Zilweku Oſihwiba: 1. Luhds\nDeewu/ lai wiꞥſch winnu wairs ne mohti/\nkur wiꞥſch tomehr jaw bebdigs un mirſtams\nZilweks irr: 13.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "As Zilweks no Seewas\ndsimmis/ dſihwo ihfu\nLaiku/ un irr pilns\nGruhtuma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wisch isaug ka Puḱḱe/\nun tohp nogreests/ wisch arri\nbehg ka Ehna/ un ne pastahw.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tattechu tu tawas Azziſ\npahr tahdu atwerr/ un welz\nmann ar tewi Teefsâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas dohd weenn Schkib-\nſtu no teem Neſchkibſteem? ne\nweens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Winna Deenas irr jaw\nnosprecstas/ winna Mehneſchu\nPuḱḱs pee tewim stahw/ tu eht\ntaim weenu Mehrki lizzis/ to pa-\nschu wisch ne pahrkahps.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nowehrsees no ta/ ka tas\nmittejahs/ kamehr wisch fanu\nDeenn itt ka Algadsisfagaida.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo weenam Rohkan irr\nZerriba/ kad tas tohp nozirsts/ ka\ntas atkat pawehrtahs/ un winna\nAtwaſfas ne mittejahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jepichu winna Saſne\neeksch Senunes pawezza ktubſt/\nun winna Zelins eekſch Pihtch-\nleem mirſt.\n"
    }
  ],
